OpenEmbedded/Yocto Project layer for EdgeAI SDK

This layer works with the latest Yocto Project release (currently 5.0+) and tracks
the stable/maintenance branches (currently "master") of the corresponding layers:

URI: git://git.openembedded.org/openembedded-core
branch: master
revision: HEAD
layers: meta

URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-ti
branch: master
revision: HEAD
layers: meta-ti-bsp, meta-ti-extras, meta-ti-test

URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-arm
branch: master
revision: HEAD
layers: meta-arm, meta-arm-toolchain

URI: git://git.openembedded.org/meta-openembedded
branch: master
revision: HEAD
layers: meta-oe, meta-networking, meta-python

URI: https://code.qt.io/yocto/meta-qt6.git
branch: 6.9
revision: HEAD

URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-arago
branch: master
revision: HEAD
layers: meta-arago-distro, meta-arago-extras

URI: https://github.com/TexasInstruments/meta-tisdk
branch: master
revision: HEAD
layers: meta-ti-foundational

